    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so selfish to keep holding on when i know i'm just a constant source of pain for them. if i actually cared about their future, wouldn't i want to remove the biggest obstacle in their way? even if it's the hardest thing i'd ever do, wouldn't it be more selfless to just... let them be free of me?",
